f="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">The Weeknd</a> （该公司也一直<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/universal-music-strip-viral-ai-generated-drake-and-the-weeknd-collaboration-from-streaming-platforms-3432055">是人工智能生成音乐的</a>牺牲品）对她“演唱”的《Starboy》的人工智能“翻唱”是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/selena-gomez-finds-ai-cover-of-the-weeknds-starboy-scary-3488137">“可怕的”</a> 。</p><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-responds-to-the-ai-generated-lost-oasis-album-3451406">瞄准了</a>今年早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-a-lost-oasis-album-created-by-ai-3432125">在网上分享的</a>人工智能生成的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a> “专辑”。 “这些该死的白痴显然有太多的时间了，”他当时说道。</p><p>其他公开反对人工智能的艺术家包括认为人工智能<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-expresses-his-fears-over-weird-ai-technology-3479746">“奇怪”的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">埃德·希兰（Ed Sheeran）</a>和认为人工智能<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blurs-damon-albarn-says-were-gonna-need-more-drugs-to-get-through-absurd-ai-3478542">“荒谬”的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/damon-albarn">达蒙·阿尔巴恩（Damon Albarn）</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-and-paris-hilton-among-metas-new-ai-chatbots-3505579">Meta 的新型人工智能聊天机器人中的 Snoop Dogg 和 Paris Hilton</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
